- Always build the irman.test* tools.
- If compiled with lirc > 0.9.3, builds the irman lirc plugin (i. e., driver).
- Add ChangeLog, AUTHORS + INSTALL to make package GNU-compatible
- Using a GNU make extension $(shell ...).

